hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'd like to send this parcel to lavestra tabletta Now, can anybody explain me what is the issue with “draconian Russian legislation against gays and lesbians”? I mean – factually, explaining what does that legislation say, and what is there draconian about it? I have no opinion on that since I do not know the content of the issue. Could somebody who knows what that legislation says explain? But, please, factually, without propagandist bombarding with buzzphrases and empty cliches – Menendez and others have already taken care of that!
